name: methylisocitrate lyase
comment: The enzyme acts on threo-Ds-2-methylisocitrate, but not on threo-Ds-isocitrate, threo-DL-isocitrate or erythro-Ls-isocitrate.

references.title: Distinction between isocitrate lyase and methylisocitrate lyase in Candida lipolytica.
Purification and properties of methylisocitrate lyase, a key enzyme in propionate metabolism, from Candida lipolytica.
